{"tid":1522852,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男子朗讀「不徇私，不畏懼，不對他人懷惡意」 即遭防暴警察包圍","createTime":"2019-08-31T14:41:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T14:51:11.000Z","uid":68738,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3fb6ee02f9606dd13bb05ef8078879f2017b72db","tid":1522852,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T14:41:49.000Z","msg":"【即時】(22:10) 防暴警察於中央圖書館及天后清場後，折返銅鑼灣渣甸街，到達燈籠洲街市後。有一名年輕男子對警察朗讀「不徇私，不畏懼，不對他人懷惡意」。他隨即遭十多名防暴警察包圍，要求查核其身份證和身上所有物品。該名男子隨即舉起雙手，但警員仍對他指罵。<br />\n<br />\n擾攘15分鐘後，警員才放行，有警員稱「依加係你懷惡意，明唔明？差人做嘢唔X洗你教。」<br />\n<br />\n獨媒記者拍攝期間，有傳媒聯絡警員稱「唔好咁多事啦，曱甴就由X得佢啦。」記者繼續採訪，再有其他警員稱「影嚟都嘥氣，成日用個cam對住我哋。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YPKXw3s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYPKXw3s.jpg&h=77136c6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/200954406608272/posts/2400287190008305?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F200954406608272%2Fposts%2F2400287190008305%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=07n8ytxkS9OF8NraT9rIu6tywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=c6bfcf74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/200954406608272/posts/2400287190008305?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"8f868d93926e67ae19a30133936c739363ce9737","tid":1522852,"uid":249721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T14:47:59.000Z","msg":"黑警=老鼠咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6efb6f6254ebb6937e523b34e03d1919eb4c8642","tid":1522852,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T14:51:11.000Z","msg":"黑警無改錯名"}]}